<paragraph blockId="4.[151,1437,1575,2033]" pageId="4" pageNumber="235">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[199,327,1934,1960]" pageId="4" pageNumber="235">Comment:</emphasis>
This species is easily identifiable by the dark brown to black pubescence on the intertegular area (sometimes extended on the anterior half of the mesoscutum) combined with the greenish metallic metasoma with orange pubescence on distal terga in both sexes.
</paragraph>
